<header class="jumbotron text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Our Restaurant</h1>
    <p class="lead">Delicious food, cozy atmosphere</p>
</header>

<body>

    <section class="py-3">
                <div id="carouselId" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li
                            data-bs-target="#carouselId"
                            data-bs-slide-to="0"
                            class="active"
                            aria-current="true"
                            aria-label="First slide"
                        ></li>
                        <li
                            data-bs-target="#carouselId"
                            data-bs-slide-to="1"
                            aria-label="Second slide"
                        ></li>
                        <li
                            data-bs-target="#carouselId"
                            data-bs-slide-to="2"
                            aria-label="Third slide"
                        ></li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img
                                src="/Banner/banner1.jpg"
                                class="w-100 d-block"
                                alt="First slide"
                            />
                            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img
                                src="/Banner/banner2.jpg"
                                class="w-100 d-block"
                                alt="Second slide"
                            />
                            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img
                                src="/Banner/banner3.jpg"
                                class="w-100 d-block"
                                alt="Third slide"
                            />
                            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button
                        class="carousel-control-prev"
                        type="button"
                        data-bs-target="#carouselId"
                        data-bs-slide="prev"
                    >
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button
                        class="carousel-control-next"
                        type="button"
                        data-bs-target="#carouselId"
                        data-bs-slide="next"
                    >
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                
    </section>

    <section class="py-3">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="dropdown">
                    <button
                        class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle"
                        type="button"
                        id="triggerId"
                        data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                        aria-haspopup="true"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                    >
                        STORES
                    </button>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="triggerId">
                        {{#each branches}}
                            <a class="dropdown-item" href="#">{{BranchName}}</a>
                        {{/each}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">RESERVATION</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="py-3">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 align-self-center">
                <div class="card border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">Meaning</h4>
                        <h2 class="card-title">The Flavor of the Sun</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">
                           The name "SuShiX" is a combination of the "X" from "Excellent" and "SuShi," 
                           a traditional dish from the Land of the Rising Sun. It symbolizes "The Flavor of the Sun."
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                           This reflects SuShiX's aspiration to bring diners a refreshing breeze from the land of cherry blossoms—Japan—through 
                           the exploration and experience of its unique traditional cuisine.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 align-self-center">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
                    <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/Banner/inside.jpg" alt="Title" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>
    
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 align-self-center">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
                    <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/Banner/inside2.jpg" alt="Title" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 align-self-center">
                <div class="card border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">History</h4>
                        <h2 class="card-title">"The Best Sushi Restaurant at</h2>
                        <h2 class="card-title g-2">an Affordable Price"</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">
                           The journey began with the establishment of a chain of restaurants, 
                           with the first branch opening in 2020 
                           in Ho Chi Minh City. Since then, SuShiX has consistently upheld the philosophy of creating 
                           an "International sushi restaurant with the best quality at truly affordable prices."
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text">
                           Each SuShiX branch spans a total area of 3,000m², 
                           accommodating up to 1,000 guests, 
                           and offers over 100 diverse sushi dishes inspired by the culinary traditions of Japan.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="container text-center py-3">
        <div class="card border-0">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title">OUR PRINCIPLES</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                <i class="fas fa-utensils fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Fresh Ingredient</h3>
                <p>Prioritizing fresh ingredients, healthy and seasonally.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                <i class="fas fa-utensils fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Delicious Food</h3>
                <p>Experience the taste of our exquisite dishes and drinks made with top quality ingredients.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                <i class="fas fa-wine-glass-alt fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Unique Experience</h3>
                <p>Diners can admire the cooking process with our show kitchen</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-3">
                <i class="fas fa-concierge-bell fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h3>Excellent Service</h3>
                <p>Our staff is dedicated to providing you with the best dining experience.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-3">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2>OUR MENU</h2>
